{"id":140,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":140,"title":"D&C 136","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 136"],[".studyIntro",["i","The word and will of the Lord, given through President Brigham Young at Winter Quarters, the camp of Israel, Omaha Nation, on the west bank of the Missouri River, near Council Bluffs, Iowa."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.1-16"},"1–16"],", How the camp of Israel is to be organized for the westward journey is explained;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.17-27"},"17–27"],", The Saints are commanded to live by numerous gospel standards;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.28-33"},"28–33"],", The Saints should sing, dance, pray, and learn wisdom;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.34-42"},"34–42"],", Prophets are slain so that they might be honored and the wicked condemned."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.1","order":"06.05.136.17085"},["b","1"],"The Word and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Will"],"of the Lord concerning the Camp of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Israel"],"in their journeyings to the West:"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.2","order":"06.05.136.17086"},["b","2"],"Let all the people of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"The"],"Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints, and those who journey with them, be organized into companies, with a covenant and promise to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"keep"],"all the commandments and statutes of the Lord our God."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.3","order":"06.05.136.17087"},["b","3"],"Let the companies be organized with captains of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"hundreds"],", captains of fifties, and captains of tens, with a president and his two counselors at their head, under the direction of the Twelve",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"Apostles"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.4","order":"06.05.136.17088"},["b","4"],"And this shall be our",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"covenant"],"—that we will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"walk"],"in all the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"ordinances"],"of the Lord."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.5","order":"06.05.136.17089"},["b","5"],"Let each company provide themselves with all the teams, wagons, provisions, clothing, and other necessaries for the journey, that they can."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.6","order":"06.05.136.17090"},["b","6"],"When the companies are organized let them go to with their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"might"],", to prepare for those who are to tarry."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.7","order":"06.05.136.17091"},["b","7"],"Let each company, with their captains and presidents, decide how many can go next spring; then choose out a sufficient number of able-bodied and expert men, to take teams, seeds, and farming utensils, to go as pioneers to prepare for putting in spring crops."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.8","order":"06.05.136.17092"},["b","8"],"Let each company",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"bear"],"an equal proportion, according to the dividend of their property, in taking the poor, the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"widows"],", the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"fatherless"],", and the families of those who have gone into the army, that the cries of the widow and the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"fatherless"],"come not up into the ears of the Lord against this people."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.9","order":"06.05.136.17093"},["b","9"],"Let each company prepare houses, and fields for raising",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"grain"],", for those who are to remain behind this season; and this is the will of the Lord concerning his people."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.10","order":"06.05.136.17094"},["b","10"],"Let every man use all his influence and property to remove this people to the place where the Lord shall locate a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"stake"],"of Zion."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.11","order":"06.05.136.17095"},["b","11"],"And if ye do this with a pure heart, in all faithfulness, ye shall be blessed; you shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"blessed"],"in your flocks, and in your herds, and in your fields, and in your houses, and in your families."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.12","order":"06.05.136.17096"},["b","12"],"Let my servants Ezra T. Benson and Erastus Snow organize a company."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.13","order":"06.05.136.17097"},["b","13"],"And let my servants Orson Pratt and Wilford Woodruff organize a company."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.14","order":"06.05.136.17098"},["b","14"],"Also, let my servants Amasa Lyman and George A. Smith organize a company."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.15","order":"06.05.136.17099"},["b","15"],"And appoint presidents, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"captains"],"of hundreds, and of fifties, and of tens."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.16","order":"06.05.136.17100"},["b","16"],"And let my servants that have been appointed go and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"teach"],"this, my will, to the saints, that they may be ready to go to a land of peace."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.17","order":"06.05.136.17101"},["b","17"],"Go thy way and do as I have told you, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"fear not"],"thine enemies; for they shall not have power to stop my work."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.18","order":"06.05.136.17102"},["b","18"],"Zion shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"redeemed"],"in mine own due time."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.19","order":"06.05.136.17103"},["b","19"],"And if any man shall seek to build up himself, and seeketh not my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"counsel"],", he shall have no power, and his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"folly"],"shall be made manifest."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.20","order":"06.05.136.17104"},["b","20"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"Seek ye"],"; and keep all your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"pledges"],"one with another; and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"covet"],"not that which is thy brother’s."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.21","order":"06.05.136.17105"},["b","21"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"Keep"],"yourselves from evil to take the name of the Lord in vain, for I am the Lord your God, even the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"God"],"of your fathers, the God of Abraham and of Isaac and of Jacob."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.22","order":"06.05.136.17106"},["b","22"],"I am he who",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"led"],"the children of Israel out of the land of Egypt; and my arm is stretched out in the last days, to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"save"],"my people Israel."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.23","order":"06.05.136.17107"},["b","23"],"Cease to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"contend"],"one with another; cease to speak",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"evil"],"one of another."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.24","order":"06.05.136.17108"},["b","24"],"Cease",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"drunkenness"],"; and let your words tend to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"edifying"],"one another."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.25","order":"06.05.136.17109"},["b","25"],"If thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"borrowest"],"of thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"neighbor"],", thou shalt",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_25c"},"restore"],"that which thou hast borrowed; and if thou canst not repay then go straightway and tell thy neighbor, lest he condemn thee."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.26","order":"06.05.136.17110"},["b","26"],"If thou shalt find that which thy neighbor has",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"lost"],", thou shalt make diligent search till thou shalt",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"deliver"],"it to him again."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.27","order":"06.05.136.17111"},["b","27"],"Thou shalt be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"diligent"],"in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"preserving"],"what thou hast, that thou mayest be a wise",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_27c"},"steward"],"; for it is the free gift of the Lord thy God, and thou art his steward."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.28","order":"06.05.136.17112"},["b","28"],"If thou art",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"merry"],",",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"praise"],"the Lord with singing, with music, with",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_28c"},"dancing"],", and with a",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_28d"},"prayer"],"of praise and",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_28e"},"thanksgiving"],"."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.29","order":"06.05.136.17113"},["b","29"],"If thou art",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"sorrowful"],", call on the Lord thy God with supplication, that your souls may be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_29b"},"joyful"],"."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.30","order":"06.05.136.17114"},["b","30"],"Fear not thine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"enemies"],", for they are in mine hands and I will do my pleasure with them."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.31","order":"06.05.136.17115"},["b","31"],"My people must be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"tried"],"in all things, that they may be prepared to receive the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"glory"],"that I have for them, even the glory of Zion; and he that will not",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_31c"},"bear"],"chastisement is not worthy of my kingdom."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.32","order":"06.05.136.17116"},["b","32"],"Let him that is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"ignorant"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_32b"},"learn"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_32c"},"wisdom"],"by",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_32d"},"humbling"],"himself and calling upon the Lord his God, that his",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_32e"},"eyes"],"may be opened that he may see, and his ears opened that he may hear;"],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.33","order":"06.05.136.17117"},["b","33"],"For my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"Spirit"],"is sent forth into the world to enlighten the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_33b"},"humble"],"and contrite, and to the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_33c"},"condemnation"],"of the ungodly."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.34","order":"06.05.136.17118"},["b","34"],"Thy brethren have rejected you and your testimony, even the nation that has",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"driven"],"you out;"],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.35","order":"06.05.136.17119"},["b","35"],"And now cometh the day of their calamity, even the days of sorrow, like a woman that is taken in travail; and their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"sorrow"],"shall be great unless they speedily repent, yea, very speedily."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.36","order":"06.05.136.17120"},["b","36"],"For they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_36a"},"killed"],"the prophets, and them that were sent unto them; and they have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_36b"},"shed"],"innocent blood, which crieth from the ground against them."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.37","order":"06.05.136.17121"},["b","37"],"Therefore, marvel not at these things, for ye are not yet",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"pure"],"; ye can not yet bear my glory; but ye shall behold it if ye are faithful in keeping all my words that I have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_37b"},"given"],"you, from the days of Adam to Abraham, from Abraham to Moses, from Moses to Jesus and his apostles, and from Jesus and his apostles to Joseph Smith, whom I did call upon by mine",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_37c"},"angels"],", my ministering servants, and by mine own voice out of the heavens, to bring forth my work;"],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.38","order":"06.05.136.17122"},["b","38"],"Which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_38a"},"foundation"],"he did lay, and was faithful; and I took him to myself."],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.39","order":"06.05.136.17123"},["b","39"],"Many have marveled because of his death; but it was needful that he should",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_39a"},"seal"],"his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_39b"},"testimony"],"with his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_39c"},"blood"],", that he might be",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_39d"},"honored"],"and the wicked might be condemned."],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.40","order":"06.05.136.17124"},["b","40"],"Have I not delivered you from your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_40a"},"enemies"],", only in that I have left a witness of my name?"],["div",{"id":"41","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.41","order":"06.05.136.17125"},["b","41"],"Now, therefore, hearken, O ye people of my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_41a"},"church"],"; and ye elders listen together; you have received my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_41b"},"kingdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"42","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.42","order":"06.05.136.17126"},["b","42"],"Be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_42a"},"diligent"],"in keeping all my commandments, lest judgments come upon you, and your faith fail you, and your enemies triumph over you. So no more at present. Amen and Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.1a","order":"06.05.136.17127"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-will-of"},"TG God, Will of"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.1b","order":"06.05.136.17129"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.32.32-35"},"D&C 133:32 (32–35)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/a-of-f/1.10"},"A of F 1:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.2a","order":"06.05.136.17131"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.1.1-4"},"D&C 20:1 (1–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/115.4"},"115:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.2b","order":"06.05.136.17133"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/41.5.5-6"},"D&C 41:5 (5–6)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/56.2.2-3"},"56:2 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.3a","order":"06.05.136.17135"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.21.21-27"},"Ex. 18:21 (21–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.3b","order":"06.05.136.17137"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostles"},"TG Apostles"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.4a","order":"06.05.136.17139"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/covenants"},"TG Covenants"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.4b","order":"06.05.136.17141"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scripture